Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.79,0:00:14.80,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:14.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:18.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.19,0:00:22.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:26.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:30.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:33.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:36.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:40.00,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.09,0:00:44.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:48.00,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.39,0:00:50.96,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:54.68,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:59.24,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:02.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:11.00,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:13.11,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.11,0:01:14.95,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.95,0:01:18.59,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:24.79,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,200.389)}The Demonic Assassin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:24.79,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(507.167,670.389)}the Eerie Fly Man
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.51,0:01:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Look alive already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.84,0:01:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Bye-bye!\N- Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two! C'mon, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.35,0:01:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's lots of cars,\Nso watch yourselves at the crosswalk!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.39,0:01:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Look both ways before you cross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.03,0:01:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.77,0:01:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:59.02,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}Tachibana Racing Club
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastards...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We barely touched him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's their fault\Nfor being so slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.29,0:02:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, wait!\N- Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch them, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Goro.\NLeave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Taki, you handle things here!\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it more speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! Stop, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Catch us if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon and catch us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You people... Don't you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You hit a child back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You call yourself human?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan's overpopulated anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be better off with a\Nfew less people in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the man we've\Nbeen waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The blood that runs through\Nhis veins is as cold as ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Capture that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform him into Fly Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never find him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Hiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine, too. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad it wasn't serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No more need to worry, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be discharged\Nin two or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro,\Nyou really don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't done anything wrong.\NAll right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, can I stay here\Nuntil Hiroshi feels better?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, right, Hiroshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Complete the surgery quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly Man is the cyborg that\Nwill defeat the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The surgery is\Nproceeding smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I found out where the\Nhit-and-run driver lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to kill Ichimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Where can I find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see your demonic blood is\Nalready racing for the kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Administer this drug to the members\Nof the Tachibana Racing Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What will this do to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who have taken that drug
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,can be controlled with the\Ncommand sound waves you emit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Can they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You hate Ichimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You wish to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means that anyone who takes\Nthat drug will also be consumed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,by a desire to kill\NIchimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think about how\NI want to kill him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the people around him\Nwill feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Fly Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, and kill Ichimonji Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I will kill him,\Nno matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I have everything I need!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They're making us wait a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the lady of the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be here very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The maid told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:09:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the one claiming\NOsamu hit a child and ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe\Nhe's capable of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what proof do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son hit a\Nchild with his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Pure hearsay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not raise\Nmy Osamu that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right... your maid said\NOsamu's been gone for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you worried about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not especially.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone to a friend's\Nhouse to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust him, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, don't let your\Ncoffee get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a truly fine Italian roast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see we're not\Ngetting through to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... very fine coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.26,0:10:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink up, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We might never drink\Nsomething so fancy ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you very much.\N- Help yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- She creeps me out.\N- Come on, she can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She's creepy,\Nbut her coffee is excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chairman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Pops!\N- Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, Yuri... what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at their eyes.\NThey're not in their right mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki... be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?\NWho's that over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown\Nyourself, Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:20.61,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider...\Nwe'll finish this later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... where's he gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a fierce opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we really have to tie them all up?\NPoor things...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika. They aren't in\Ntheir right minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They tried to kill us, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ammonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll wake them up, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.57,0:14:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chairman, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri! You're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.16,0:14:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we tied up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't remember\Nwhat happened before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Untie me, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're better!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The drug will remain\Neffective for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:15:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,At least for the next two\Ndays, your command sound waves
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,will make Tachibana Tobei—Ichimonji\NHayato's most trusted comrade...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,An assassin out for his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, why don't we administer\Nthis drug to every person in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,First, administer it to Goro and\NEmi, the remaining club members.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Fly Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to feed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You have to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro... you still feel\Nresponsible, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just eat up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.43,0:15:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your food, Goro?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi's gonna bring it by later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go ahead and eat, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro! I brought your food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have our lunch, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro! Emi! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill Ichimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:38.96,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an7}Tachibana Auto Corner
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Closed today."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you two are back already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All finished at the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Taki? Yeah, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, Hiroshi is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Goro and Emi check him out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Hiroshi isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did Hiroshi go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did anyone see Hiroshi go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The chairman and Yuri are\Nstill under Shocker's control!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello? Hello?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:18:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm scared! \N- It's okay. Hayato is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Take care of the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get the monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Take her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.72,0:20:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you all right?\N- You two, get in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Try me, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish you this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:22:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Flip-Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.67,0:22:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.58,0:22:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're back with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey...\N- Where in the world are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.81,0:22:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they're\Nfinally back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.88,0:22:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.89,0:22:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were\Nin the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.66,0:22:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all better now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.84,0:22:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But are you sure they're\Nall back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:22:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.44,0:22:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.79,0:22:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.54,0:22:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone tell me! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.74,0:23:01.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato,\Nthe Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:04.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,had foiled Doctor Shinigami's latest\Nterrible plan, involving Fly Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:08.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker would\Nsurely attack again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.08,0:23:10.80,Cont,,0,60,160,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.97,0:23:15.10,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.21,0:23:16.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:18.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monster-bird Pranodon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.97,0:23:21.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It uses Taki and Emi of\Nthe Tachibana Racing Club
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:24.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to try to assassinate\NIchimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:26.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.31,0:23:30.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Monstrous Bird\NPranodon Attacks!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:30.90,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx85\fs105\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(208,690)}The Monstrous Bird\NPranodon Attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.90,0:23:40.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.32,0:23:43.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.32,0:23:45.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.28,0:23:48.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.83,0:23:50.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.70,0:23:52.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:54.37,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:55.82,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.26,0:23:58.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.26,0:24:03.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.98,0:24:07.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.51,0:24:11.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.62,0:24:15.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Demonic Assassin,\Nthe Eerie Fly Man